Date: 1999-01-11

Title: From Yang-Mills Field to Solitons and back again

Comments: Latex2e with amssymb.sty, amsfonts.sty, a4.sty

Lecture delivered at XXXVI Summer School on Subnuclear Physics at Erice inSeptember 1998. It contains a brief reflection on the development of QFT inlate sixties and a discussion of the role of solitons in realistic fieldtheoretic models.